# Email HQ / MailPilot API (only if the UI is NOT served from the same host as Express).
# Local dev: leave unset — Vite proxies /api → http://localhost:5055 (run server in ../server).
# Frontend-only Vercel project: set to your API base, e.g. https://your-app.vercel.app
# VITE_EMAIL_HQ_API=

# Optional: Indeed-style + multi-board job rows on /apply (JSearch via RapidAPI — Google Jobs index).
# Subscribe: https://rapidapi.com/letscrape-6bRBa3QguO5/api/jsearch — copy your app key here.
VITE_RAPIDAPI_KEY=

# Optional: 2-letter country for JSearch (default us).
# VITE_JSEARCH_COUNTRY=us
